        "rt_title": "ONE DESIGN, DUAL PURPOSE",
        "rt_text1": "The Grand Soleil 44 was a great challenge for Cantiere del Pardo. Designed by Matteo Polli, a designer renowned for his high-performance hull lines, the 44-footer completes the Performance range by showing a well-balanced relationship between size and performance. During navigation maneuvers, the owner and guests can take advantage of all the necessary space, for the comfort of the interiors and for the livability of the deck.",
